Package: uncanny
Type: Package
Title: researching the uncanny valley phenomenon
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Martin Schmettow
Maintainer: Martin Schmettow <schmettow@web.de>
Description: The uncanny valley phenomenon is a disruption in
    emotional judgement of faces on the humano-mechanical spectrum.
    Faces that are almost human-like cause the strongest aversion.
    This package provides simulation functions for the cognitive
    process under the theory of category confusion.
LazyData: TRUE
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    stringr,
    plyr,
    ggplot2,
    shiny,
    mascutils

RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
